			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2783860">
									

<p>I dislike this on a fundamental level. I don't think it's poorly written, but it's such a straight port of Universe Prime sensibilities over to Alexvya that it really feels like it ceases to be about them and what makes them entertaining and transitions into a Flintstones-esque parody of Uni tropes. I can totally see other people enjoying it as a matter of interdimensional magitech hijinks, but it's definitely not for me.</p>

