<p>As far as I understand it's supposed to be Carthage winning the second punic war, and the perspective this article is coming from is a world that is perilous. From other documents I've seen this is consistent with the world as at least some of them wrote it. This article is supposed to be seen as sort of being written by an unreliable narrator, with a progression as it goes through. I can try to edit down some of the ritualistic stuff.</p>
